// Plugin protocol v1 for clawpatrol's Terraform-style external plugins.
//
// One subprocess per plugin source. The gateway spawns the subprocess
// via hashicorp/go-plugin, fetches its Manifest, and registers virtual
// *config.Plugin entries for each declared (credential / tunnel /
// endpoint) type. At request time the gateway hands inbound conns to
// the plugin over the HandleConn bidi stream; endpoints that need an
// upstream connection through a tunnel go through Dial.
